Introduction

Project Title : Assignment Tracking System 

Domain

The system falls under the Education domain, focusing on to support students in managing their academic tasks and deadlines more effectively.

Problem Statement

Many students struggle to manage multiple assignments across different modules using complex platforms such as Blackboard. 
These systems often lack simple task tracking features, which results in missed deadlines, poor time management, and increased academic stress.

System Purpose

The purpose of this system is to provide a centralized and user-friendly platform where students can:
Add and manage assignments
Set deadlines
Receive automated reminders
Track their progress
This system complements existing LMS platforms by focusing specifically on assignment tracking and personal productivity.

Individual Scope

This project is feasible as an individual project because it focuses on core functionalities without requiring complex integrations.
The system will include:

User authentication (login/register)
Assignment management (add, edit, delete)
Deadline tracking
Reminder notifications

Advanced features such as AI recommendations or LMS integration may be considered as future enhancements but are not part of the current scope.
